criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  T1-T2 stage breast cancer

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  axillary lymph node metastasis;

          -  previous surgery on the ipsilateral axilla;

          -  neoadjuvant chemo-radiotherapy;

          -  presence of primitive lymphedema of the arm;

          -  allergy to Iodine, thyroid disease, renal and hepatic impairment (for issues related
             to Indocyanine Green)

          -  pregnancy;

          -  patients refusing to participate in the study.
